PROCEDURE:-  
1. Open the C# Windows application Project and add a form to it.  
2. Open the Tool Box, Click the DataGridView tool and place it on the Form by dragging the mouse.  
3. Add a datasource for the project and choose the datasource type as database.  
4. Select the data connections and database object as the table.  
5. Run the application. The records will be displayed in the Datagridview. 
